        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued June 8 at 5:24PM CDT until June 8 at 6:00PM CDT by NWS Amarillo TX</headline>
        <description>At 523 PM CDT, severe thunderstorms were located along a line
extending from 12 miles east of Stinnett to 5 miles south of Borger,
moving southeast at 15 mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts and quarter size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor damage to roofs, siding, and trees is possible. Hail
damage to vehicles is expected.

Locations impacted include...
Skellytown and Borger.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
